Spring is arriving at last in SA, and we've got just the thing for all the braai masters in the making to start braai season and get rid of the wintry lockdown blues. When you buy the Sunday Times at Pick n Pay on the following Sundays in September, you'll get a free braai gift: Even better, if you then SMS the word BRAAI, your till-slip number and your name to 40730, you'll stand a chance of winning one of 10 Megamaster Heritage Series 900 Crossover Freestanding Charcoal Braais.